.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: romance, animation, martial-arts, drama, spy
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, entrepreneur, chef, hip-hopcher, freelancer
The people use 5 different means of transport: airplane, van, motorbike, tram, boat
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: soul, hip-hop, folk, jazz, house
City: berlin, rome, hamburg, prague, new-york

1. the videographer is the person watching romance movies
2. the entrepreneur is the person traveling to berlin
3. the fan of soul is the person watching animation movies
4. the chef is the fan of hip-hop
5. the person watching animation movies is to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies
6. the person driving the airplane is the person traveling to new-york
7. the person driving the van is the person watching drama movies
8. the fan of folk is in the middle
9. the hip-hopcher is on the far left
10. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome
11. the person driving the van is to the left or right of the person traveling to prague
12. the person driving the tram is the fan of jazz
13. the freelancer is the person driving the boat
14. the hip-hopcher is to the left or right of the person watching spy movies

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Job	|   hip-hopcher	|    chef	|     videographer	|    entrepreneur	|    freelancer	|
| Movie-Genre		|    drama	|      spy	|      romance	|     martial-arts	|     animation	|
| Music-Genre	|     house	|      hip-hop	|      folk	| jazz	|     soul	|
| Transport		|     van	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| tram	|   parliament	|
| City		|     rome	|     prague	|     new-york	|     berlin	|     hamburg	|
